text: Thomas Wren is the name of: *Thomas Wren (footballer) (born 1907), English footballer *Thomas Wren (Nevada politician) (1826–1904), American Republican politician *Tommy Wren (born 1976), American Democrat politician in Arkansas *Thomas Thurston Thomas (born 1948), American science fiction author *Thomas Wren (priest) (1632–1679), Archdeacon of Ely
